            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 font-display">ECOSISTER (PNRR)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-semibold mb-2">Spoke 3: Green manufacturing for a sustainable economy</p>
              <p class="text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-300">
                Developing data-driven and lean-based solutions for sustainable production planning and control systems.
                Focus on Engineering-to-Order (ETO) and high-automation manufacturing contexts.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="neo-card neo-hover p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="neo-icon-box flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
