              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-1 font-display">RL-AutoLog</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-semibold mb-2">FAR Dipartimentale DIEF 2023 (Winner)</p>
              <p class="text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-300">
                Reinforcement Learning for Highly Automated Intra-Logistics Processes: A Simulation-based Approach.
                Combining discrete event simulation with RL algorithms for logistics optimization.
              </p>
            </div>
